text: Ra na ta uniharumathi kunai dosa lagcha jo tapa'inko pasama a'umchan ki tapa'inle uniharuko nimti savariko prabandha garidinus ani tapa'inle javapha dinuhuncha ki ma timiharuko savariko nimti kehi pani pa'unna, ta uniharu duhkhada avasthama amkhabata amsu baga'umdai pharkanchan ki uniharusita kharca garnako nimti kehi pani upalabdha chaina
